Voot, launched in March 2016, forms the digital arm of Viacom 18, Network 18 Media. It is Viacom18's advertising-led video-on-demand platform that is available as an app for Apple  and Android users, and a website for desktop consumption.
Voot is available only in India, and hosts over 40,000 hours of video content that includes shows from channels like MTV, Nickelodeon and Colors. Content is also available in multiple languages like Kannada, Marathi, Bengali, Gujarati and Tamil.
